description:
Music player for Subsonic servers with modern Material You interface
Youamp is a music player for Subsonic servers with a modern Material You interface and a high level of privacy, which is ensured by the absence of trackers, advertising and analytics. The source code is open, so anyone can make Youamp better.

The following functionality is currently supported:
• View a list of artists, albums and playlists
• Search for artists, albums and songs
• Play music
• Add an unlimited number of Subsonic servers
